  "description": "He speaks to slot machines. He's here with his chainsaw to CUT YOU A DEAL! Elon Muskrat is selling his new casino and YOU can be the lucky buyer. From “star storyteller Josh Languedoc” (Liz Nichols), author of Rocko and Nakota (★★★★★), this show explores what floats on the surface of power and what hides beneath it.",
